                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "4. The rules for “1 and 1” foul shooting in basketball are as follows. The shooter gets to try to make a basket from the foul line. If he succeeds, he gets another try. More precisely, he make 0 baskets by missing the first time, 1 basket by making the first shot and xsmissing the second one, or 2 baskets by making both shots. "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                191,
                702,
                803,
                785
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Let n be a fixed integer, and suppose a player gets n tries at “ 1 and 1” shooting. Let "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "N _ { 0 }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": ", "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "N _ { 1 }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": ", and "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "N _ { 2 }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "be the random variables recording the number of times he makes 0, 1, or 2 baskets, respectively. Note that "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "N _ { 0 } + N _ { 1 } + N _ { 2 } = n"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": ". Suppose that shots are independent Bernoulli trails with probability "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "p"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "for making a basket. "
                    }
                ]
