                            },
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "| | \\cdot | | _ { b }"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": ". His argument is based on the equivalency of all norms in a finite dimensional space, namely for any two norms "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
