                "math_content": "\\delta | | u | | _ {b} \\leq | | u | | _ {a} \\leq \\frac {1}{\\delta} | | u | | _ {b}.",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/440e4c573370dda235750c6f0008e08a367087e5f15a7de5397549026ea06fab.jpg"
