            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Do you agree with his argument? If yes, please give a detailed proof of the following theorem: If a scheme is stable, namely (3) holds for one particular norm (e.g. the "
